# `{{ project_name }}` — Agent Operating Guide

This file orients you (an AI coding agent) to the conventions of a
trestle-scaffolded Databricks-Apps-ready Rust service. Read it before editing.

## Mental model

**Proto is the source of truth.** Every API surface, model type, server handler
trait, and TypeScript client method is generated from
`proto/{{ project_name | snake_case }}/v1/*.proto`. You should change `.proto`
files first, run `just regen`, and then implement the new handler — never the
other way around.

